 quality, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/460790/extras/40bc351aabe786e6b56f7c70b830bded.webp?t=1763677459\" width=18 height=18 /></span>   <strong>English and Japanese Voice Overs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely switch languages and subtitles at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/460790/extras/be1748a96deaadf8751758e858099146.poster.avif?t=1763677459\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/460790/extras/be1748a96deaadf8751758e858099146.webm?t=1763677459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/460790/extras/be1748a96deaadf8751758e858099146.mp4?t=1763677459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
